nodes.text: Frozen Out! is a short comic story published in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.34.

In this issue's all-new The Clone Wars comic adventure, 'Frozen Out', Obi-Wan and Jar Jar are forced to land on a frrrr-reezing planet! Stuck between a squadron of battle droids and a herd of rampaging wampas, how will our heroes possibly escape? There's only one way to find out…
